ActiveProspect,is,a,marketing,automation,platform,for,generating,and,qualifying,leads,ActiveProspect,enables,businesses,to,integrate,existing,conversion,CRM,systems,as,well,as,extend,the,platform,to,rd,party,applications,To,integrate,with,the,platform,ActiveProspect,exposes,their,core,API,The,LeadConduit,API,enables,developers,to,return,information,on,campaigns,leads,statistics,account,management,and,sales,information,The,API,accepts,HTTP,POSTS,requests,in,JSON,formats,and,uses,a,users,s,LeadConduit,login,with,HTTP,basic,authentication